Recent Interiorshooting for @bfsdesign. Bfs d found again a way to celebrate the idea of a rustic barn for @thebarnberlin in a modern and urban way. ⁠
Thonet chairs with a light cane work as a reference to coffeehouses and the wooden walls representing the barn look. ⁠
.⁠
Detail shot made with  #sonyalpha6000 and my old analogue nikon 50mm lens with an adapter. ⁠

Something better than a cookie filled with peanut butter and jam? Yes, two cookies. 🍪🍪⁠
I learned to love this combination in the UK / Ramsgate with toast, with bananas, actually with everything, just fill it with crunchy peanut butter and jam and enjoy.⁠
⁠
This is another detail I photographed during the Interior shooting with @bfsdesign at @thebarnberlin at the #sonycenter #berlin.⁠
